//        <2=> 2: 10 = Both overflow and underflow for saw waves and trough for triangle waves and complementary PWM mode are counted and skipped
//        <3=> 3: 11 = Both overflow and underflow for saw waves and both crest and trough for triangle waves and complementary PWM mode are counted and skipped
//    </combo>
